The TIRTIR Milk Skin Toner is a highly concentrated, vegan-friendly toner designed to deeply moisturize and brighten the skin, promoting a radiant and healthy glow. The 50ml size offers a convenient option for those seeking a travel-friendly version of this skincare product.

How to use?
After cleansing, apply an appropriate amount of the toner to a cotton pad or directly onto your palms. Gently pat it onto your face and neck, avoiding the eye area. For optimal results, follow with your regular skincare routine.
